  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 text-center">
          
          <h2>The Story Behind the Project</h2>
          <p class="lead text-muted">
            Have you ever stared into your fridge, full of random ingredients, and thought, "I have nothing to eat"? We have. That moment is the reason this project was born. We saw a disconnect between the food we had and the meals we could imagine. This leads to unnecessary food waste, last-minute trips to the store, and money spent on takeout.
          </p>
          <hr class="my-5 bg-secondary">

          <h2>What We Do</h2>
          <p class="lead text-muted">
            Our AI Recipe Recommender flips the script on traditional cooking. Instead of asking you to find a recipe and then buy the ingredients, we ask: <strong class="text-white">"What do you already have?"</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="lead text-muted">
            By telling us the ingredients, spices, and even the equipment you have on hand, our smart system intelligently filters through countless possibilities to suggest delicious recipes you can make right now. We believe that the best meal is the one you can create with the resources you already possess.
          </p>
          <hr class="my-5 bg-secondary">

          <h2>Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="lead text-muted">
            Our vision is a world with less food waste. We aim to empower home cooks everywhere to be more creative, confident, and sustainable in the kitchen. This tool is more than just a recipe finder; it's a step towards a more conscious and resourceful way of living, proving that you can save the planet and your wallet, starting with what's in your fridge.
          </p>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
